item.title: Psalm 3 | Sleep Psalms with Bishop T.D. Jakes
item.description: Podcast Description Fall asleep to special Psalm devotionals at https://www.sleeppsalms.com Tonight's prayer is from Psalms 3:3. Welcome to "Sleep Psalms with Bishop T.D. Jakes," a tranquil oasis of serenity for your weary soul. In each episode, you'll embark on a soothing journey guided by the wisdom of the most popular book of the Bible, the book of Psalms. Bishop T.D. Jakes' calming voice and gentle prayers will lull you into a peaceful state of mind, perfect for restful sleep or deep meditation.
